# Stack Constraints

## Frontend — allowed only
- Next.js 14 (App Router) — no Pages Router
- shadcn/ui primitives — no MUI, Chakra, Ant Design, or Mantine
- Tailwind CSS — no CSS Modules, styled-components, or Emotion
- TanStack Query (`@tanstack/react-query`) — no SWR, Apollo Client, or raw fetch in components
- React Hook Form + Zod — no Formik, no uncontrolled forms
- Lucide React — no Heroicons, FontAwesome, or react-icons

## Backend — allowed only
- NestJS 10 — no Express raw, Fastify, or Hono
- Prisma ORM — no TypeORM, Drizzle, Sequelize, or raw SQL queries
- PostgreSQL 16 — no MySQL, SQLite, or MongoDB
- `nestjs-pino` — no Winston, Bunyan, or console.log in services
- `@willsoto/nestjs-prometheus` + `prom-client` — no custom metric endpoints
- `@sentry/node` via SentryService — never import @sentry/node directly in domain code

## Infra
- Docker Compose — all services must be runnable via `docker compose up -d`
- No Kubernetes, no serverless functions

## Forbidden patterns
- `any` type in TypeScript — use `unknown` and narrow
- `console.log` in services — use injected PinoLogger
- Raw SQL (`$queryRaw`, `$executeRaw`) — use Prisma model methods
- Direct `fetch()` in React components — use TanStack Query hooks
- Importing `@sentry/node` outside `SentryService`
